{"id":232721016,"title":"生命","content":"逆流而上，是活魚的權利，是義務\n\n順流而下，是死魚的福利，是命運\n\n我是\n\n半邊活魚的血肉，半邊死魚的屍體\n\n在歷史的洪流中，載浮載沉\n\n拼死掙扎著\n\n垂死掙扎的憤恨\n\n死纏爛打的無奈\n\n剪不斷，理還亂\n\n梳不開，放又纏\n\n活生生的不願向命運低頭，死沉沉的隨波逐流\n\n當這些成了習慣\n\n成了日常\n\n誰還記得我們壞掉之前的模樣\n\n\n\n✎﹏🅒🅷🅾︎🅒🅾︎🅻🅰︎🆃🅔.","excerpt":"逆流而上，是活魚的權利，是義務，順流而下，是死魚的福利，是命運，我是，半邊活魚的血肉，半邊死魚的屍體，在歷史的洪流中，載浮載沉，拼死掙扎著，垂死掙扎的憤恨，死纏爛打的無奈，剪不斷，理還亂，梳不開，放又","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-19T15:34:12.392Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-19T15:34:12.392Z","commentCount":1,"likeCount":10,"tags":["HIDE_THUMBNAIL"],"topics":["新詩","創作","心情","文字","日常"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"佛光大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[],"postAvatar":""}